  "detailed_description": "Traverse dynamic terrains and engage in an endless deathmatch with a grappling-hook-equipped tank. Outlast and outmaneuver your opponents in Grapple Tanks, a 2D multiplayer shooter game playable with up to 4 people.<br><br>Grapple Tanks is playable with 2-4 players. Play online with friends or join a public match!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Dynamic Terrain</h2>Break through walls, floors and ceilings that are in your way.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2679340/extras/e1584be431d4070cf358b9d410db2400.poster.avif?t=1704733255\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2679340/extras/e1584be431d4070cf358b9d410db2400.webm?t=1704733255\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2679340/extras/e1584be431d4070cf358b9d410db2400.mp4?t=1704733255\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Weapons</h2>Pick up weapon drops and deal devastating damage.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2679340/extras/a71d479900f9805efe7dd4174203d12b.poster.avif?t=1704733255\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2679340/extras/a71d479900f9805efe7dd4174203d12b.webm?t=1704733255\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2679340/extras/a71d479900f9805efe7dd4174203d12b.mp4?t=1704733255\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Powerups</h2>Use powerups to gain a formidable advantage against your opponents.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2679340/extras/2847a9de535c6f9f55d5be5c2e389dea.poster.avif?t=1704733255\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2679340/extras/2847a9de535c6f9f55d5be5c2e389dea.webm?t=1704733255\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2679340/extras/2847a9de535c6f9f55d5be5c2e389dea.mp4?t=1704733255\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "Traverse dynamic terrains and engage in an endless deathmatch with a grappling-hook-equipped tank. Outlast and outmaneuver your opponents in Grapple Tanks, a 2D multiplayer shooter game playable with up to 4 people.<br><br>Grapple Tanks is playable with 2-4 players. Play online with friends or join a public match!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Dynamic Terrain</h2>Break through walls, floors and ceilings that are in your way.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2679340/extras/e1584be431d4070cf358b9d410db2400.poster.avif?t=1704733255\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2679340/extras/e1584be431d4070cf358b9d410db2400.webm?t=1704733255\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2679340/extras/e1584be431d4070cf358b9d410db2400.mp4?t=1704733255\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Weapons</h2>Pick up weapon drops and deal devastating damage.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2679340/extras/a71d479900f9805efe7dd4174203d12b.poster.avif?t=1704733255\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2679340/extras/a71d479900f9805efe7dd4174203d12b.webm?t=1704733255\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2679340/extras/a71d479900f9805efe7dd4174203d12b.mp4?t=1704733255\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Powerups</h2>Use powerups to gain a formidable advantage against your opponents.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai